      • validateServiceAttributes

        boolean validateServiceAttributes​(String token,
                                  String validatorClass,
                                  Set values)
                           throws SMSException,
                                  SSOException,
                                  RemoteException
        Validates service configuration attributes.
        Parameters:
        token - Single Sign On token.
        validatorClass - validator class name.
        values - Values to be validated.
        Returns:
        true of values are valid.
        Throws:
        SMSException - if value is not valid.
        SSOException - if single sign on token is in valid.
        RemoteException - if remote method cannot be invoked.
